nodes.text: Tram Pump Station 726 was one of many pump stations that supported the tram system in the Spire of Zakuul. In 3631 BBY Senya Tirall, T7-O1 and The Commander passed the station on their way to Platform 6.
Tram Pump Station 726 appears as an area on Zakuul during Chapter 7: The Lady of Sorrows of the Star Wars: The Old Republic: Knights of the Fallen Empire expansion.
